{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be futuristic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Quantum Design Labs</title>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&family=Exo+2:wght@400;700&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e60000; /* Deep Red */\n            --secondary-color: #330000; /* Darker Red/Maroon */\n            --background-color: #0d0d0d; /* Very Dark Gray */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --accent-color: #ff4d4d; /* Lighter Red for accents */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 60px 0;\n        }\n\n        h1, h2, h3 {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            text-align: center;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--brand-color));\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(230, 0, 0, 0.5);\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n        }\n\n        header .container {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        .logo {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            letter-spacing: 3px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 30px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease, text-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><polygon points=\"0,0 100,0 50,100\" style=\"fill:%23330000;opacity:0.6;\"/><polygon points=\"0,100 100,100 50,0\" style=\"fill:%23e60000;opacity:0.4;\"/></svg>') center center / cover no-repeat;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color) 0%, var(--brand-color) 100%);\n            opacity: 0.8;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .hero .container {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        .services, .portfolio, .contact {\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(230, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .services::before, .portfolio::before, .contact::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--background-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 50%, var(--brand-color) 100%);\n            opacity: 0.5;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .services .container, .portfolio .container, .contact .container {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .service-grid, .portfolio-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item, .portfolio-item {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid rgba(230, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover, .portfolio-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(230, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i, .portfolio-item img {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            text-align: left;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item h3 {\n            text-align: left;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(230, 0, 0, 0.5);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input:focus,\n        .contact-form textarea:focus {\n            outline: none;\n            border-color: var(--accent-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer .container {\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        /* Animations */\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        .fade-in {\n            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            h1 { font-size: 2.5em; }\n            h2 { font-size: 2em; }\n            h3 { font-size: 1.5em; }\n            .hero h1 { font-size: 3em; }\n            .hero p { font-size: 1.2em; }\n            header .container { flex-direction: column; }\n            nav ul { margin-top: 20px; }\n            nav ul li { margin: 10px 0; }\n            .service-grid, .portfolio-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            .container { width: 95%; }\n            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5em; }\n            .hero p { font-size: 1em; }\n            .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea { width: calc(100% - 10px); padding: 10px; }\n            .contact-form button { width: 100%; }\n        }\n\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"logo\">QUANTUM</div>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#services\">Services</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#portfolio\">Portfolio</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero fade-in\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>QUANTUM DESIGN LABS</h1>\n            <p>Crafting Tomorrow's Digital Realities</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Core Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item fade-in\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-robot\"></i>\n                    <h3>AI-Driven UX Design</h3>\n                    <p>Leveraging AI to understand user behavior and create intuitive, responsive interfaces.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item fade-in\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-code\"></i>\n                    <h3>Futuristic Web Development</h3>\n                    <p>Building cutting-edge websites with dynamic animations and seamless user experiences.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item fade-in\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-palette\"></i>\n                    <h3>Generative Art & Visuals</h3>\n                    <p>Creating unique, algorithmically generated visual assets for branding and digital products.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"portfolio\" class=\"portfolio\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Featured Projects</h2>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-grid\">\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item fade-in\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/e60000/ffffff?text=Project+Chrono\" alt=\"Project Chrono\">\n                    <h3>Project Chrono</h3>\n                    <p>A time-bending application interface with dynamic data visualizations.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item fade-in\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/330000/ffffff?text=Nexus+Core\" alt=\"Nexus Core\">\n                    <h3>Nexus Core</h3>\n                    <p>Interactive branding for a next-gen tech company, focusing on connectivity.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item fade-in\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/e60000/ffffff?text=Orbital+Studio\" alt=\"Orbital Studio\">\n                    <h3>Orbital Studio</h3>\n                    <p>A creative platform with a space-themed aesthetic and advanced rendering.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Let's Build the Future</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-form fade-in\">\n                <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Transmission</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2077 Quantum Design Labs. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Pioneering the digital frontier with vision and precision.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach((element, index) => {\n            element.style.animationDelay = `${index * 0.2}s`;\n        });\n\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {\n            e.preventDefault();\n            alert('Message sent! We will respond shortly. (This is a simulation.)');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n\n        // Smooth scrolling for anchor links\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}